Q2 . Write testcases for lift 

Functional Testing
Basic functionality verify karte hain:

User floor button press kare → lift correct floor pe jaye

Up/Down button kaam kare

Door open/close properly ho

Floor display sahi show kare

Lift current direction follow kare (up/down logic)

Example Test Case:

Input: Floor 3 press

Expected: Lift floor 3 pe ruk jaye

Negative Testing

Invalid button press (multiple random press)

Same floor button baar-baar press

Overload hone par lift move na kare

Door forcefully close karne pe error handle ho
Edge Case Testing

Lift top floor pe hai → up button press

Lift ground floor pe hai → down button press

Simultaneous requests (multiple floors)

Power fluctuation
Performance Testing

Peak hours me response time

Multiple requests handle karna

Waiting time optimize ho

6. Security Testing

Unauthorized access (maintenance mode)

Restricted floors access control

Emergency override misuse na ho

Usability Testing
Buttons clearly visible ho

Braille support ho

Voice announcement clear ho

Elderly-friendly design
8. Safety Testing (VERY IMPORTANT)

Door obstruction pe lift close na ho

Emergency alarm kaam kare

Power failure pe backup system

Free fall prevention system

🔁 9. Regression Testing

New changes ke baad old functionality break na ho

All floors and buttons re-test

